high level options
- shift is capital for the opposite keyboard and
  special for adjacent
  - this is great for traditional typing
  - this isn't great for one handed hotkeys
- modifiers are on an adjacent only layer
  - again this isn't great for one handed hotkeys

one hand hotkey applies only to the right hand
right hand has four free slots
shift, command, control, option

